                <div class="two-third last">
                 <p>As we move towards the platinum era, I welcome all of you to the amazing world of Josephites.				Thank you for visiting the website of St Joseph's Convent Higher Secondary School, 				Chittaranjan.  We have arrived at our third year of our ongoing mission to re-launch the 				legacy of St Joseph's, and we greatly appreciate the support from the thousands of 				spirited alumni, invested community partners, fantastic parents, well wishers and 				associates.</p>				<p>				As you read through the pages of this site, you will learn more about the wonderful				students and our School where our prayers and our teachings make our students go out 				into the world with the strength, not only to excel in their professional aspirations, but to 				remain as beautiful human beings.				St Joseph's is a symbol of progressive and quality education. Our motto, ♦virtue alone 				ennobles♦ captures the essence of our spirit. Following the principles of our patron St 				Joseph's, we are a model of obedience, hard work, just and uprightness for all those 				who come and learn here. In our school, children gain an all-round education and 				achieve their potential not just in the academic field but also in the field of sports and 				creative arts.				</p>				<p>				Our school fosters the all round growth and development of students to their fullest 				potential; spiritually, intellectually, culturally and physically. We guide our students in the 				development of a sound value system and inculcate in them a deep love for their culture 				and country. 				The education imparted is characterized by thoroughness, high principles and freedom. 				The students are helped to grow in responsibility, self reliance and human maturity so 				that they find meaning and purpose in their lives and are inspired to live and work for 				building up a just and fraternal society.				Most importantly we want to provide a bigger platform to the students as well as the 				alumni and explore their budding talents through this website. I invite all the students 				especially the alumni to visit the website and to be a part of the Josephite family.				</p>				<p>					At the school, we are a team of dedicated teachers and staff, committed to the welfare					of the children in our care. For us teaching is a passion and a calling. The importance of 					instilling good values in our students is our prime objective, as Ralph Waldo Emerson 					has so aptly said, •What lies behind us and what lies before us are small compared to 					what lies within us.•					We feel privileged to work with your children.  Our students are well behaved, 					cooperative, and strive to do well.  I am proud of the efforts our students exhibit.  I am 					equally proud of the superb commitment our staff has to your children as well. 					Every great dream begins with a dreamer. Always remember, you have within you the 					strength, the patience, and the passion to reach for the stars to change the world, said 					Harriet Tubman, so Josephites go for it and reach the stars					I pray for all the blessings over every small step that we take towards growth and 					progress.				</p>


				<strong>With best wishes</strong><br/>
				<h6>Principal</h6>
				<h6>St. Joseph's Convent Higher Secondary School</h6>
				<h6>Chittaranjan.</h6>
